name: NANI
description: Nani is a token created to empower pop culture within an original and fantastical anime-style universe. The project revolves around a world that is constantly growing and evolving, filled with hundreds of unique characters. With a rich and immersive narrative, Nani aims to bring this universe to life through the development of comics, animations, and an original animated series. More than just a token, Nani is the heart of a new entertainment franchise.
